high_descs: Go across the room to the counter next to the fridge.
Pick up the salt shaker next to the spatula.
Go across the room to the table.
Set the salt shaker down on the table in front of the bread.
Turn around and walk to the counter next to the fridge.
Pick up the salt shaker on the counter.
Turn to the right and go across the room to the table.
Set the salt shaker down to the left of the other salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Take two salt shakers to the table.

high_descs: Turn around, then turn right to go to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Pick up the rightmost salt on the counter.
Turn around, then turn left, the turn left, then right to face the table with the coffee maker.
Place the salt on the table, beside the bread.
Turn around and return to the counter beside the fridge.
Pick up the salt on the counter.
Turn around, then turn left, the turn left, then right to face the table with the coffee maker.
Place the salt on the table, to the left of the other salt.
anns.task_desc: Put the two salts on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink then turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the salt shaker that's to the right of the other salt shaker.
Turn around and take half a step then turn left and walk to the table.
Put the salt shaker under the loaf of bread.
Go back to where you got the first salt shaker.
Pick up the other salt shaker.
Walk back over to where you put the first salt shaker.
Put this salt shaker to the left of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on the table.
